        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Bound to @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.shadowcountSial1]{Shadowcount Sial} (his casket is her door): when Sial would take damage, she can absorb it instead (his life link). At 0 HP she is <strong>banished to the Plane of Shadow, not slain</strong> — Sial cannot call her back for a day. Resistance 10 cold; resistance 5 physical (except holy).</p>"
